  "title": "Loot Journal: Pickup Notifier",
  "description": "Ultimate item pick-up notifier featuring rich animations, full theming support, customizable layouts, and powerful filtering options!",
  "body": "<a href=\"https://lunapixel.studio/bisect\"><img width=100% src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/obscuria/image/upload/v1769702795/bisect.png\"></a>\n\n<center>\n    <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/loot-journal-fabric\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"Fabric\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Fabric-213f5c?style=for-the-badge\"></a> \n    <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/loot-journal\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"Forge\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Forge-213f5c?style=for-the-badge\"></a>\n    <a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/loot-journal-neoforge\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"NeoForge\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/badge/Neo_Forge-213f5c?style=for-the-badge\"></a>\n    <a href=\"https://discord.gg/jSHHJSUWdY\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img alt=\"Discord\" src=\"https://img.shields.io/discord/899742852681191444?style=for-the-badge&logo=discord&logoColor=white&label=&labelColor=231C25&color=3d215c\"></a>\n</center>\n\n<br>\n\n### <center>Loot Journal is a client-side mod that enhances item pickups with smooth, animated notifications, smart stacking, and full visual customization. Track your own and nearby players' pickups in real time, tweak every detail in-game, and enjoy a clean, immersive UI.</center>\n\n<br>\n\n<center><img width=80% src=https://res.cloudinary.com/obscuria/image/upload/v1769699368/header/features.png></center>\n\n<br>\n\n<table>\n    <tr>\n        <td width=\"60%\">\n            <img width=\"100%\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/u0aVYsI.gif\">\n        </td>\n        <td width=\"40%\">\n            <h1>Smooth Pickup Flow</h1>\n            <p>Clean, animated pickup notifications slide naturally from the edge of the screen, blending seamlessly into gameplay. Smart stacking, merging, and positioning logic keeps everything readable, while special effects highlight rare finds. Fully supports both items and experience.</p>\n        </td>\n    </tr>\n</table>\n\n<br>\n\n<table>\n    <tr>\n        <td width=\"40%\">\n            <h1>Visual Themes</h1>\n            <p>Choose from multiple built-in visual themes, each with its own style and layout. Every theme can be tweaked individually, and entirely new ones can be added through resource packs, allowing complete visual freedom.</p>\n        </td>\n        <td width=\"60%\">\n            <img width=\"100%\" src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1613/690/lj1-jpg.jpg\">\n        </td>\n    </tr>\n</table>\n\n<br>\n\n<table>\n    <tr>\n        <td width=\"60%\">\n            <img width=\"100%\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/iup6WPg.gif\">\n        </td>\n        <td width=\"40%\">\n            <h1>Player Tracking</h1>\n            <p>See what nearby players are picking up in real time. Track friends, discover rare finds, or monitor activity around you. Fully configurable with player filters — and players can stay hidden using invisibility or a carved pumpkin. Works on vanilla servers!</p>\n        </td>\n    </tr>\n</table>\n\n<br>\n\n<table>\n    <tr>\n        <td width=\"40%\">\n            <h1>In-Game Config</h1>\n            <p>A fully accessible and user-friendly configuration system lets you fine-tune every aspect of the mod. Adjust layout, positioning, animations, sounds, and filtering directly in-game with immediate feedback.</p>\n        </td>\n        <td width=\"60%\">\n            <img width=\"100%\" src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1612/362/4-jpg.jpg\">\n        </td>\n    </tr>\n</table>\n\n<br>\n\n<table>\n    <tr>\n        <td width=\"60%\">\n            <img width=\"100%\" src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1612/363/5-jpg.jpg\">\n        </td>\n        <td width=\"40%\">\n            <h1>Polished UX Details</h1>\n            <p>Designed for clarity and comfort. Entries pulse when updated, large pickup bursts are neatly aggregated, and total item counts are tracked — including items inside shulkers, sacks, and other containers. Everything works together to keep your screen informative without clutter.</p>\n        </td>\n    </tr>\n</table>\n\n<br>\n\n<center><img width=80% src=https://res.cloudinary.com/obscuria/image/upload/v1769699408/header/more-from-obscuria.png></center>\n\n<br>\n\n<center>\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/aquamirae\"><img style=\"display: inline;\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/obscuria/image/upload/v1769702990/aquamirae.png\" width=\"45%\" /></a> \n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/obscure-tooltips\"><img style=\"display: inline;\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/obscuria/image/upload/v1769702990/obscure-tooltips.png\" width=\"45%\" /></a>\n</center>\n<center>\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/pillager-caravans\"><img style=\"display: inline;\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/obscuria/image/upload/v1769702990/pillager-caravans.png\" width=\"45%\" /></a> \n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/ars-elixirum\"><img style=\"display: inline;\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/obscuria/image/upload/v1769702990/ars-elixirum.png\" width=\"45%\" /></a>\n</center>\n<center>\n  <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/accents\"><img style=\"display: inline;\" src=\"https://i.imgur.com/quXJZzx.png\" width=\"45%\" /></a> \n  <img style=\"display: inline;\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/obscuria/image/upload/v1769702990/blank.png\" width=\"45%\" />\n</center>\n<center>\n  <a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/Obscuria\"><img style=\"display: inline;\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/obscuria/image/upload/v1769702990/patreon.png\" width=\"90%\" /></a>\n</center>\n<center>\n  <a href=\"https://discord.gg/jSHHJSUWdY\"><img style=\"display: inline;\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/obscuria/image/upload/v1769702990/discord.png\" width=\"90%\" /></a>\n</center>\n",
